    public class SeriesTableView<X,Y>
extends Control
    TableView displaying XYChart.Series data in columns.

    CSS class name: "series-table-view".

      • SeriesTableView

        public SeriesTableView(ObservableValue<ObservableList<XYChart.Series<X,Y>>> value)
        Creates a new instance of SeriesTableView displaying list of series from the given observable value, binding the dataProperty() to given observable value.

        This constructor can be used be used to bind content of this control with series rendered by an XYChart: 

         
 LineChart<Number, Number> lineChart = ...;
 SeriesTableView<Number, Number> chartTable = new SeriesTableView<>(lineChart.dataProperty());
        In such case any changes of data rendered by the chart will be reflected in the table view.
        Parameters:
        value - an observable value containing list of series to be displayed
